online.search
Interface TreeProviderProtocol

All Known Implementing Classes:
CommonDriver, Search_Driver, UCTMoveSearcher
public interface TreeProviderProtocol

this interface identifies objects which cooperate with tree viewers at the moment, the actual implementation is ad-hoc, so there are no formal requirements. It is currently implemented by the standard boardspace search driver covering both alpha-beta and mcts searches
